// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3038 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 6457bd00-269c-5238-9fef-970d27e0567b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*")
